      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, though there is light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All electronic systems, including the dual-zone climate control, touchscreen navigation, and premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has a complete service history with recent brake pad replacements and a fresh oil change. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. This is a reliable, well-cared-for example that looks great in a driveway and feels even better behind the wheel. Sold with two sets of keys and all original manuals.",
